<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome on board</title>
    <style>
        .logo {
      text-align: center;
    }
.logo img {
     max-width: 200px;
      height: auto;
}

    /* CSS styles for the header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* CSS styles for the button */
    .button {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .button a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src='${process.env.BASE_URL}/assets/logo.jpeg' alt="schoolBook logo">
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Schoolbook Edu Limited</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Dear <%= fullName %>,</p>

    <p> Thank you for choosing schoolbook! We just need to verify your email address to finalize your registration process</p>
    <p>Once your email is verified, you'll gain full access to all the features and benefits of the platform</p>
    <p>If you didn't initiate this registration, please disregard this email and be rest assured that your information remains secured</p>
    <p>To complete this verification process, please click the button below</p>

    <div class="button">
        <a href="<%= magicLink %>">Verify Your Email</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>